headline: 4 Agriculture Operations Stocks to Watch Amid Positive Industry Trends
summary: Innovation and rising demand for healthy foods are fueling growth in the Agriculture - Operations industry, while challenges like input costs and trade woes linger. CTVA, DOLE, AGRO and AVO look promising.
